    "In particular, at each practice activity, a particular ChatGPT-integration approach was applied as an intervention to support students' programming learning.",
    "While these interventions will be explained in greater detail in the following section, the details on the research design and data collection are explained here.",
    "As illustrated in Fig. 1, the research design involved multiple steps, starting with a short online test during the first week of the semester via the LMS at the end of the lecture.",
    "This test, designed to measure students' prior knowledge of Python programming, consisting of 15 multiple-choice questions and was prepared by the course instructor.",
    "Importantly, this assessment has been used consistently in the course for the past 3 years, establishing its reliability as a measure of baseline knowledge."
